Class TSValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • ts.support.TSValue
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TSObject, TSPrimitive, TSReference

    public abstract class TSValue
extends java.lang.Object
    The super class for all Tscript values.

      • not

        public final TSPrimitive not()
        Perform an logic not. "this" is the oldValue. If oldValue is true, return false, else return true. OldValue are get from ToBoolean.
        Returns:
        the result of the logical not

      • negate

        public final TSNumber negate()
        Perform negate. "this" is the oldValue. If oldValue is nan, return nan, else converts its operand to Number type and then negates it
        Returns:
        the result of negate
